/* Q1. Write a DCG that accepts strings of the form u2v where u and v are strings
over the alphabet {0, 1} such that the number of 0’s in u is the same as the
number of 1’s in v. */ 

s --> one,[0],one,s,zero,[1],zero.
s --> [2].
one --> [1],one.
one --> [1].
one --> [].
zero --> [0],zero.
zero --> [].


